| BUG_01 | Back button after logout             | After logout, clicking browser back button briefly shows the products page before redirecting to login. | Login → Logout → Press browser back                   | User should stay logged out completely                        | Inventory page appears for a moment | High        |
| BUG_02 | Number input accepted in name fields | During checkout, I was able to enter only numbers in First Name and Last Name fields and continue.      | Add product → Checkout → Enter `12345` in name fields | System should show validation error                           | Checkout continues normally         | Medium      |
| BUG_03 | Sorting resets on refresh            | Selected sorting filter gets reset after refreshing the page.                                           | Select sorting option → Refresh page                  | Selected filter should remain                                 | Filter changes back to default      | Low         |
| BUG_04 | Cart badge update delay              | After removing the last item from cart, the cart badge takes a second to disappear.                     | Add item → Remove item from cart                      | Cart badge should disappear immediately                       | Badge disappears after slight delay | Low         |
| BUG_05 | Login error message could be clearer | Invalid login message works, but wording feels a bit technical and not very user friendly.              | Enter wrong username/password                         | Message should clearly guide user                             | Generic error shown                 | Low         |
| IMP_01 | Password visibility option missing   | Login page does not have show/hide password option.                                                     | Open login page and type password                     | User should be able to view password if needed                | No visibility option available      | Improvement |
| IMP_02 | Empty cart page feels incomplete     | When cart is empty, page looks plain and does not guide the user.                                       | Open cart without adding products                     | Helpful message or continue shopping suggestion should appear | Empty page with minimal info        | Improvement |
